---
title: Installing PCF on Azure Manually
owner: Ops Manager
---

Complete the following procedures to manually install Pivotal Cloud Foundry (PCF) on Azure:

1. Deploy Ops Manager. See [Deploying Ops Manager on Azure Manually](../om/azure/deploy-manual.html).

1. Configure BOSH Director. See [Configuring BOSH Director on Azure Manually](../om/azure/config-manual.html).

1. (Optional) Install the IPsec add-on. See [Installing the PCF IPsec Add-On](http://docs.pivotal.io/addon-ipsec/installing.html).

1. Deploy PAS. See [Deploying PAS on Azure](./azure-er-config.html).
